  "description" : "The protagonist chose to reincarnate as the rib of a harem-loving, cheat-powered hero destined for a happy ending!?\nThe setting is a world where you can keep reincarnating into any world you like until you`re satisfied enough to ascend. However, the popular “cheat-powered harem hero” reincarnation route is so in demand that the waiting time is 50,000 years... So, the protagonist decides on a reincarnation destination: “the rib of a harem-loving, happy-ending cheat hero”!? A thrilling isekai reincarnation tale featuring a lazy goddess in charge of isekai reincarnations and a protagonist who keeps finding loopholes to popular reincarnation destinations, leading to absurd reincarnations!\nWinner of the 8th Net Novel Award.\nSource: Takarajimasha, translated",
